<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٨٧ ... سُورَةُ الْأَعْلَى ... آياتها ١٩ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ}</span> ... نَزِّهْ رَبَّكَ ذَاكِرًا اسْمَهُ بِلِسَانِكَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْأَعْلَى}</span> ... الَّذِي لَهُ عُلُوُّ الذَّاتِ، وَعُلُوَّ القَدْرِ، وَعُلُوُّ القَهْرِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَسَوَّى}</span> ... أَتْقَنَ خَلْقَهُ، وَأَحْسَنَهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَهَدَى}</span> ... يَسَّرَ لَهُ مَا يُنَاسِبُهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَرْعَى}</span> ... الكَلَأَ الأَخْضَرَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غُثَاءً}</span> ... هَشِيمًا جَافًّا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَحْوَى}</span> ... مُتَغَيِّرًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِلَّا مَا شَاءَ اللَّهُ}</span> ... إِلَّا مَا أَرادَ اللهُ أَنْ يَنْسَخَ تِلَاوَتَهُ وَحُكْمَهُ، وَيُنْسِيَكَ إِيَّاهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِلْيُسْرَى}</span> ... لِلطَّرِيقَةِ المُيَسَّرَةِ فِي شَرِيعَتِكَ، وَحَيَاتِكَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَصْلَى النَّارَ}</span> ... يَدْخُلُهَا، وَيُقَاسِي حَرَّهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَفْلَحَ}</span> ... فَازَ، وَظَفِرَ بِالمَطْلُوبِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَزَكَّى}</span> ... طَهَّرَ نَفْسَهُ مِنَ المَعَاصِي، وَحَلَّاهَا بِالطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِنَّ هَذَا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> مِنْ قَوْلِهِ: <span class="c3">{قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّى}</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>